import { Box, Paper } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

export default function BaseComponent() {
    return (
        <Box classsName="basecomponent">
            <Paper>
               <Grid container>
                  <form>
                      <TextField label="search" type="text" variant="contained" />
                  </form>
               </Grid>
            </Paper>
        </Box>
    )
}
